Performance Review | 2025

Performance and Achievements
	•	Supported end-to-end testing for FSS AML new country rollouts (Saudi & Egypt) by organizing weekly/biweekly calls with country teams, driving concurrence on thresholds, HRG watchlists, and approvals. Ensured completion of DQA, SIT, and UAT ahead of tech go-live by year-end 2025 and tracked IGA completion for Saudi business go-live in Q1 2026.
	•	Managed BTL segmentation, tuning, and BTG batch runs for TH, MY, VN, SG, AE, and HK. Coordinated with SPOT team for sample validation and execution within planned timelines.
